TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
It's a racemate, Sir.

 

Waiter, Are there any allergenes in my dish?

Edited June 16, 2017 by Physics Student

Certainly. Examining your dish, you can see that solder is lead and tin, while the wire insulation contains fluorine.

Waiter! Isn't your chef afraid that this anti-soup will annihilate contacting with the spon and plate atoms?

Our spoon and plate atoms bend the rules of reality, space and time, just like the anti-soup.

 

Waiter, there's a communist uprising in my soup!

Da, dat why I of give it to yuo torsavich!

xaxa)))

Waiter! I didn't order soup!

Wait, you did not order soup? Too bad, you have to pay extra and twice as much.

 

Waiter, there's a fidget spinner in my soup. May I remove it?

Remove the cancer, burn it.

Waiter, there is a company ran by moneyhungry people who are ***holes which recently bought our universe in my soup! Its also asking me to buy shark cards but i dont like sharks in my soup.

WHAT!!!

waiter there is a Saturn V in my soup

Ah, that's where I placed that thing. I thought I had lost it forever.

 

Waiter! There's a lot of tensors in my soup!

*silently walking away shouting*

Waiter, there is a fractal in my soup and it is consuming the table!!!

Yes, food, We are The Fractal.

Customer external entity! Join-solve-aggregate into Us!

WHAT!

waiter there is a fork in my soup.

Of course, it's a fork. Otherwise how could spear this soup? On a spoon?

Chef, that client wants a spoon. Do we have a washed one?

NO

Spoiler

 *RUNS OUT OF BREATH*

WE DONT

------------------

Waiter! There's dank memes in my soup!

time to press the panic button

waiter!there is a Kristina Pimenova in my soup!whoever made this soup i hate you now!

That's why she employed you to clean the pool. Nobody likes swimming in soup instead of water.

Waiter! I am very glad for visiting this place. Thank you. Please, let me give you a tip. Better cross the street at green light!

Oh. Okay.

 

Waiter! There's the 88th page of something in my soup!

17 hours ago, Astrofox said:

Oh. Okay.

 

Waiter! There's the 88th page of something in my soup!

perfect. the mister on table 8 was eager to knwo what happened after what happened on page 87 that he found.

Waiter, theres a ring in my soup!

Yes-s, that's our Precious-s, in the soup of fish, so juicy-sweet. Ugly hobbitses stole it from us-s, bad, bad hobbitses. Give it back to us-s.

Deagol! What's this, in our boat? So bright and shiny...

Spoiler

Offtop. If they just gave the ring back to Gollum, it would hide it so deep, that Sau should wait 10000 years more.
